00:29:35,230 --> 00:29:37,750
I miss the time we were together.

566
00:29:37,870 --> 00:29:38,870
I wonder

567
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:40,430
how he's doing over there.

568
00:29:40,990 --> 00:29:42,990
He has started pursuing his dream.

569
00:29:43,190 --> 00:29:44,990
My prospects remain undecided.

570
00:29:55,190 --> 00:29:57,270
Can I really be admitted into a good university?

571
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:05,190
How are your studies recently?

572
00:30:05,630 --> 00:30:07,070
Do you need me to tutor you face to face?

573
00:30:11,510 --> 00:30:13,470
Happy birthday, Ling Chao.

574
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:38,030
Is it true that everyone set up his goal and dream long ago

575
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:39,510
except for me?

576
00:32:00,790 --> 00:32:01,750
Ling Chao?

577
00:32:09,230 --> 00:32:09,830
Excuse me.

578
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:11,230
This is my seat.

579
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,150
Don't be so petty.

580
00:32:13,470 --> 00:32:14,230
Let's share the seat.

581
00:32:17,830 --> 00:32:18,510
Why are you here?

582
00:32:18,510 --> 00:32:19,830
Aren't you in Yunhai?

583
00:32:20,150 --> 00:32:21,910
I was worried that someone would forget her own goal

584
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:23,990
and couldn't get over her pessimistic feelings.

585
00:32:26,470 --> 00:32:27,870
That's right.

586
00:32:28,350 --> 00:32:29,950
Everyone has his own dream.

587
00:32:30,190 --> 00:32:30,790
Only I don't have a dream.

588
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:31,910
How can I not be anxious?

589
00:32:33,150 --> 00:32:34,030
Why do you think you don't have a dream?

590
00:32:34,390 --> 00:32:35,670
Who always talked about

591
00:32:35,670 --> 00:32:37,230
going to and leaving school with me forever?

592
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:39,590
You said that in kindergarten.

593
00:32:39,670 --> 00:32:40,750
Speaking of goals,

594
00:32:41,430 --> 00:32:42,670
you set up a goal earlier than all of them.

595
00:32:43,590 --> 00:32:45,110
That's different.

596
00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:46,710
Besides,

597
00:32:46,710 --> 00:32:48,230
is it because I don't want to to go to Yunhai University?

598
00:32:48,310 --> 00:32:49,950
With my grades, there is big gap

599
00:32:49,950 --> 00:32:51,150
between Yunhai and me.

600
00:32:52,670 --> 00:32:54,190
Don't think too much.

601
00:32:54,550 --> 00:32:56,390
Just focus on one thing now.

602
00:32:57,030 --> 00:32:57,630
Do you

603
00:32:58,430 --> 00:32:59,590
want to go to Yunhai University?

604
00:33:07,470 --> 00:33:08,870
Since you said yes,

605
00:33:10,030 --> 00:33:11,150
just go forward bravely.

606
00:33:14,470 --> 00:33:16,230
When you were a kid, your godmother always said that

607
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:17,870
you learned everything slower than others, right?

608
00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:19,670
But when it comes to eating,

609
00:33:19,910 --> 00:33:21,430
you eat faster than anyone else, don't you?

610
00:33:23,070 --> 00:33:24,990
How can you comfort me like this?

611
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:26,750
Alright.

612
00:33:27,310 --> 00:33:28,350
I mean,

613
00:33:29,150 --> 00:33:30,270
since childhood,

614
00:33:30,590 --> 00:33:32,190
you've been able to do the things

615
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:33,550
which you want to finish.

616
00:33:34,990 --> 00:33:36,470
Just like when you were admitted into No.1 High School

617
00:33:36,470 --> 00:33:37,510
after overcoming so many difficulties.

618
00:33:38,590 --> 00:33:39,430
This time,

619
00:33:40,030 --> 00:33:41,070
you can make it, too.

620
00:33:44,830 --> 00:33:45,510
Can I...

621
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,230
really make it?

622
00:33:49,710 --> 00:33:50,870
I don't know whether others can make it.

623
00:33:53,430 --> 00:33:54,910
But your luck in exams is really good.

624
00:33:55,510 --> 00:33:56,150
So,

625
00:33:57,230 --> 00:33:58,710
just go forward bravely.

626
00:33:59,830 --> 00:34:00,950
I'll wait for you in Yunhai.

627
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:19,750
What are you doing?

628
00:34:20,270 --> 00:34:21,630
I'm writing down my own dream.

629
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:22,750
Xue said that

630
00:34:22,790 --> 00:34:24,150
we could encourage ourselves by doing this.

631
00:34:24,989 --> 00:34:26,270
But this is someone else's desk.

632
00:34:29,870 --> 00:34:30,750
Then let's leave now.

633
00:34:30,750 --> 00:34:31,989
I can buy you a cake.

634
00:34:31,989 --> 00:34:32,830
Let's celebrate your birthday.

635
00:34:32,830 --> 00:34:33,429
Let's go.

636
00:34:36,429 --> 00:34:37,190
At this hour,

637
00:34:37,190 --> 00:34:38,429
the cake shop is closed.

638
00:35:03,670 --> 00:35:05,190
Ling Chao, happy birthday.

639
00:35:07,310 --> 00:35:09,070
No one eats a Wife Cake to celebrate his birthday.

640
00:35:09,870 --> 00:35:11,470
Just make do with it.

641
00:35:11,510 --> 00:35:13,270
Besides, it has a good meaning.

642
00:35:13,270 --> 00:35:15,390
Maybe you can really get a wife after eating it.

643
00:35:16,710 --> 00:35:18,150
I might as well find some fish flesh

644
00:35:18,150 --> 00:35:19,110
in the Fish-flavoured Shredded Pork.

645
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:20,710
Wait.

646
00:35:20,830 --> 00:35:21,670
Make a wish first.

647
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:25,350
But there are no candles.

648
00:35:39,670 --> 00:35:40,270
All right.

649
00:35:42,110 --> 00:35:45,590
Happy birthday to you.

650
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:46,830
Happy...

651
00:35:47,670 --> 00:35:48,470
So soon?

652
00:35:49,470 --> 00:35:51,110
It looks like you decided what wish to make long ago.

653
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:51,790
What wish did you make?

654
00:35:52,230 --> 00:35:53,750
I hope that you can be admitted into your ideal university.

655
00:35:56,510 --> 00:35:57,710
You're lying.

656
00:35:57,790 --> 00:35:58,390
Forget it if you don't want to tell me.

657
00:35:58,390 --> 00:35:59,310
Come on. Have some cake.

658
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:03,390
Where are you going?

659
00:36:27,110 --> 00:36:28,230
Ling Chao, look.

660
00:36:28,990 --> 00:36:30,190
What era is it now?

661
00:36:30,990 --> 00:36:33,190
You're still playing these tricks   aimed at kids.

662
00:36:33,270 --> 00:36:33,910
No.

663
00:36:33,910 --> 00:36:35,350
It's true. Look.

664
00:36:39,270 --> 00:36:40,990
I regret not reading more books.

665
00:36:41,030 --> 00:36:43,870
All I can think about now is "How beautiful".

666
00:36:44,790 --> 00:36:45,550
Yes.

667
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:50,550
How beautiful.

668
00:37:16,430 --> 00:37:17,150
Ling Chao,

669
00:37:17,150 --> 00:37:18,630
you've been admitted into college.

670
00:37:18,630 --> 00:37:20,070
But I still have to suffer for a year.

671
00:37:20,070 --> 00:37:22,030
You texted me during the day, which affected my study.

672
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:23,390
You called me at night, which disturbed my rest.

673
00:37:23,390 --> 00:37:24,390
Do you understand?

674
00:37:34,110 --> 00:37:34,990
No wonder.

675
00:37:34,990 --> 00:37:37,030
Even though so many girls have asked our master for a date recently,

676
00:37:37,030 --> 00:37:38,350
he has made no response.

677
00:37:38,390 --> 00:37:40,590
It turns out he likes someone with a bad temper.

678
00:37:41,430 --> 00:37:42,870
You have no idea.

679
00:37:42,910 --> 00:37:43,950
Actually, this girl

680
00:37:44,030 --> 00:37:46,750
is our master's child bride.

681
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:51,510
You're back from begging alms.
